 : With the considerable increase of AI applications, AI is being increasingly:
 : used to solve optimization problems in engineering. In the past two        :
 : decades, the applications of artificial intelligence in power systems have :
 : attracted much research. This book covers the current level of applications:
 : of artificial intelligence to the optimization problems in power systems.  :
 : This book serves as a textbook for graduate students in electric power     :
 : system management and is also useful for those who are interested in using :
 : artificial intelligence in power system optimization.                      :
